{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1124141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "唉，虽然我家不怎么提门禁的事，但我感觉我们是一类家庭，patpat", "timestamp": 1613929606, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124142, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "憋说了，我也如此哈哈哈哈。一般我就说在学校工作室加班通宵…", "timestamp": 1613929648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124147, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实这种事情向洞友求助很无解，因为别的家庭的沟通方式很难用到自己家庭中。我每次因为和父母沟通的问题向洞友求助以后，都觉得信心大增，结果每次真的和父母沟通时，又觉得非常无力，因为家庭的基础关系不同。如果我提“别的家庭怎样怎样”，我爸妈就会反问我“我们就那么不如别的父母吗？”", "timestamp": 1613929720, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124151, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "都23了还走读？", "timestamp": 1613929967, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124155, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 好感谢你跟我说了这么多，我觉得你说得对，大家的家庭环境终归是不太一样的，别人的经验很难套用，但是我也很想从境遇一样的同学那里获得理解和鼓励，让我知道我想自由安排出行不是因为我是个坏孩子/不检点……", "timestamp": 1613930188, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124158, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我也试过，后来我家长又开始担心我的健康了，他们好操心啊", "timestamp": 1613930237, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124161, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 真实，我爸还曾说“和别人家比咱们家可是很开放的了”，我只能怼一个你不了解别的家庭就不要judge…我就是多吵架，然后我妈老说管不了我了…", "timestamp": 1613930266, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124162, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我老和我妈开玩笑说我出去租房了（我也有赚足够钱租房），但还是懒得整…哈哈", "timestamp": 1613930360, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124163, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我老和我妈开玩笑说我出去租房了（我也有赚足够钱租房），但还是懒得整…哈哈", "timestamp": 1613930386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124166, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 如果我说要去租房他们就会说家不够你住的吗别浪费那个钱哈哈，北京房子好贵本北京人也租不起", "timestamp": 1613930531, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124168, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 是的哈哈哈哈，我妈就说，你才租不起呢", "timestamp": 1613930618, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124169, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不过给洞主支招的话就说在学校加班好了，万能", "timestamp": 1613930663, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124171, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 感谢👍", "timestamp": 1613930866, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124188, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "天啊这太令人窒息了吧", "timestamp": 1613935147, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124232, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我很好奇你门禁是几点", "timestamp": 1613951919, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1124303, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 也许一种方法是和家人说明白你在外面的时候身边是有靠谱的人能保护你的安全的(比如领着见过家长的npy哈哈哈哈哈哈)", "timestamp": 1613954011, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1125018, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 八点。。", "timestamp": 1613970079, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1125227, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这也太早了…", "timestamp": 1613972837, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1126799, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 221147, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我十点", "timestamp": 1613995239, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 221147, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "想问北京的走读的朋友们如何和家里人说要在外面过夜，我都23了回家一直有门禁时间，家人因为我的性别而担心我的人身安全，每天都要早早回去，回得晚了家长甚至会开车来接，严重影响日常交际和恋爱，我又不擅长编谎圆过去，大家都是怎么跟家人沟通的呢", "timestamp": 1613929547, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1613995240, "url": "", "vote": {}}}